{"pageProps":{"wordpressPage":{"id":229,"date":"2009-08-08T20:58:12","date_gmt":"2009-08-08T20:58:12","guid":{"rendered":"http://admin.pascalegirardin.art/?post_type=project&#038;p=229"},"modified":"2020-02-02T21:02:05","modified_gmt":"2020-02-02T21:02:05","slug":"yul-sha-jdz-2","status":"publish","type":"project","link":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/en/project/yul-sha-jdz-2/","title":{"rendered":"YUL/SHA/JDZ"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"featured_media":147,"menu_order":0,"template":"","categories":[21,32,36,28],"polylang_current_lang":"en_CA","polylang_translations":[{"locale":"fr_CA","id":173}],"acf":{"size":"5","options_size":{"size":"5"},"align":"right","options_align":{"align":"right"},"subtitle":"Festival Montagne Rouge","place":"Ste-Adèle","dates":"2008","flexible_content":[{"acf_fc_layout":"text","text_content":"<p>Las Vegas, March 2008.<br />\n<em>Following a long day’s work installing an art mural inside the Mirage Casino, I stepped out to shop for Converse All-Star © sneakers. At the shoe store, I spotted a pair with a a fingerprint pattern and bought them on the spot without trying them, as my shoe size hasn’t changed since my first purchase in 1978.</em></p>\n<p>New York, May 2009.<br />\n<em>I was walking down a busy Manhattan street when a man ran up to me, pointing at my feet: “ Excuse me! Excuse me!&#8230; Your shoes… I designed them !! ”. Both R., an artistic director for an interior design agency in Miami, and I were passing through the city. We exchanged our business cards, both happy to have met.</em></p>\n<p>Jingdezhen, November 2012.<br />\n<em>After spending 3 months wandering the dusty streets of the Sculpture Factory, working on a porcelain chandelier for a client in Shanghai, I decide to mold and slip-cast my now old shoes, in fine porcelain. Upon my return home, I ship R. a gold-plated pair. Moved by this gift he tells me that they are his trophy, for all the work that went behind the designing of these shoes.</em></p>\n"},{"acf_fc_layout":"slider","images":[{"ID":154,"id":154,"title":"","filename":"SAM_2232_web.jpg","filesize":384097,"url":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2232_web.jpg","link":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/sam_2232_web/","alt":"","author":"1","description":"","caption":"","name":"sam_2232_web","status":"inherit","uploaded_to":0,"date":"2020-01-24 17:24:38","modified":"2020-01-26 22:18:57","menu_order":0,"mime_type":"image/jpeg","type":"image","subtype":"jpeg","icon":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/wp/wp-includes/images/media/default.png","width":1440,"height":1920,"sizes":{"thumbnail":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2232_web-150x150.jpg","thumbnail-width":150,"thumbnail-height":150,"medium":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2232_web-225x300.jpg","medium-width":225,"medium-height":300,"medium_large":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2232_web-768x1024.jpg","medium_large-width":768,"medium_large-height":1024,"large":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2232_web-768x1024.jpg","large-width":768,"large-height":1024,"1536x1536":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2232_web-1152x1536.jpg","1536x1536-width":1152,"1536x1536-height":1536,"2048x2048":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2232_web.jpg","2048x2048-width":1440,"2048x2048-height":1920}},{"ID":155,"id":155,"title":"","filename":"SAM_2239_web.jpg","filesize":330709,"url":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2239_web.jpg","link":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/?attachment_id=155","alt":"","author":"1","description":"","caption":"","name":"sam_2239_web","status":"inherit","uploaded_to":435,"date":"2020-01-24 17:24:39","modified":"2023-01-05 18:53:14","menu_order":0,"mime_type":"image/jpeg","type":"image","subtype":"jpeg","icon":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/wp/wp-includes/images/media/default.png","width":1440,"height":1080,"sizes":{"thumbnail":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2239_web-150x150.jpg","thumbnail-width":150,"thumbnail-height":150,"medium":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2239_web-300x225.jpg","medium-width":300,"medium-height":225,"medium_large":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2239_web-768x576.jpg","medium_large-width":768,"medium_large-height":576,"large":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2239_web-1024x768.jpg","large-width":1024,"large-height":768,"1536x1536":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2239_web.jpg","1536x1536-width":1440,"1536x1536-height":1080,"2048x2048":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2239_web.jpg","2048x2048-width":1440,"2048x2048-height":1080}},{"ID":156,"id":156,"title":"","filename":"SAM_2243_web.jpg","filesize":231066,"url":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2243_web.jpg","link":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/sam_2243_web/","alt":"","author":"1","description":"","caption":"","name":"sam_2243_web","status":"inherit","uploaded_to":0,"date":"2020-01-24 17:24:40","modified":"2020-01-26 22:18:52","menu_order":0,"mime_type":"image/jpeg","type":"image","subtype":"jpeg","icon":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/wp/wp-includes/images/media/default.png","width":1440,"height":1080,"sizes":{"thumbnail":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2243_web-150x150.jpg","thumbnail-width":150,"thumbnail-height":150,"medium":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2243_web-300x225.jpg","medium-width":300,"medium-height":225,"medium_large":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2243_web-768x576.jpg","medium_large-width":768,"medium_large-height":576,"large":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2243_web-1024x768.jpg","large-width":1024,"large-height":768,"1536x1536":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2243_web.jpg","1536x1536-width":1440,"1536x1536-height":1080,"2048x2048":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/SAM_2243_web.jpg","2048x2048-width":1440,"2048x2048-height":1080}}]},{"acf_fc_layout":"text","text_content":"<p><em>YUL/SHA/JDZ</em> traces the path between two individuals united by a brand of shoes which are no longer associated to a specific country of origin, but rather belong to a global culture. The original sneakers, designed in the U.S., manufactured in China and distributed throughout the world are a fitting representation of freedom, American style. Their ceramic counterparts, slipcast in fine porcelain in Jingdezhen, have been transposed in a contemporary art gallery context. The vernacular symbol of casual urbanity and world culture embodied by the All Star © becomes transcoded into an art relic.</p>\n<p>The reproduction of these shoes is a gesture that goes beyond the mere act of replication, since the wear of the soles and the specific folds around the ankles are mine. The stories multiply with each slipcasting: a friend’s, a culture and mine. Simultaneously acting as a starting point, a reference and an encounter, these shoes are a reminder that my world is both shrinking and growing.</p>\n"},{"acf_fc_layout":"one_image_row","size":"9","image":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/pascale-girardin-shoes_3.jpg","align":"center"},{"acf_fc_layout":"one_image_row","size":"5","image":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/app/uploads/2020/01/pascale-girardin-shoes_4.jpg","align":"left"}]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/wp-json/wp/v2/projects/229"}],"collection":[{"href":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/wp-json/wp/v2/projects"}],"about":[{"href":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/wp-json/wp/v2/types/project"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https://admin.pascalegirardin.art/wp-json/wp/v2/media/147"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https://admin.pascalegirar